summary: For Hogwarts House Sorting: Vader, captain Rex, commander Cody, Pre Vizsla and Bo-Katan, please :)
question: For Hogwarts House Sorting: Vader, captain Rex, commander Cody, Pre Vizsla and Bo-Katan, please :)
answer:
Vader - Hufflepuff. Anakin is a Hufflepuff so Vader is what you get when a Hufflepuff goes bad. I will die on this hill.

Rex - Gryffindor with Hufflepuff tendencies.

Cody - Probably the same as Rex. I suspect most clones were either Gryffindor or Hufflepuff, simply because of how they were raised/trained.

Pre Vizsla - Probably Slytherin, but Gryffindor is also a possibility.

Bo-Katan - I don’t really have a good sense of her character, but I’m going to go with either Slytherin or Gryffindor.

summary: As may be apparent by now, I don’t actually own a photography lightbox of any sort. Not only does this encourage me to regularly...
caption: As may be apparent by now, I don’t actually own a photography lightbox of any sort. Not only does this encourage me to regularly seek out new locations for my photo shoots, it means I get to experiment with all kinds of light, both natural and artificial. Aside from the first one, which involved the flash option on my camera, all of these were taken under a typically-bright porch light at about 12:30 am, and I was delighted by the shadowy yet clear images I got as a result!
